flowchart TD
    SP[SharePoint Online<br/>System of record<br/>Original files remain here]
    ING[Azure Function<br/>Submission discovery<br/>Metadata scan only]
    SB[Azure Service Bus<br/>Submission queue<br/>Primary workload buffer]
    ORCH[Durable Functions Orchestrator<br/>One workflow per submission]

    OUT[SharePoint Results<br/>CSV by form type]
    ST[Azure Storage<br/>Durable runtime state]
    YAML[Yaml Definitions<br/>Known form types<br/>Known attachment types<br/>Validation rules]

    subgraph WF[Activities coordinated by the Orchestrator]
        EXT_FORM[Activity: ExtractFormText<br/>Single form file]
        EXT_ATTACH[Activity: ExtractAttachmentText<br/>Fan-out per attachment]
        ANALYZE[Activity: AnalyzeForm<br/>Determine form type<br/>Extract key form facts]
        REL{Relevant submission?}
        CLASS_ATTACH[Activity: ClassifyAttachment<br/>Fan-out per attachment]
        VALIDATE[Activity: ValidateSubmission<br/>Generic YAML-driven engine]
        WRITE[Activity: WriteResults]
    end

    OCR[Azure Document Intelligence<br/>OCR / text extraction]
    AI[Azure OpenAI / Foundry<br/>Constrained classification<br/>Structured extraction<br/>Soft judgment]
    PY[Deterministic Python Rules<br/>Date windows<br/>Required docs<br/>Exact rule enforcement]

    %% Main business flow
    SP --> ING
    ING -->|Submission manifest| SB
    SB -->|Queued submission| ORCH

    ORCH --> EXT_FORM
    ORCH --> EXT_ATTACH

    EXT_FORM --> OCR
    EXT_ATTACH --> OCR

    EXT_FORM --> ANALYZE
    ANALYZE --> REL

    REL -->|No| WRITE
    REL -->|Yes| CLASS_ATTACH

    EXT_ATTACH --> CLASS_ATTACH
    CLASS_ATTACH --> VALIDATE
    ANALYZE --> VALIDATE

    VALIDATE --> WRITE
    WRITE --> OUT

    %% Supporting dependencies
    ANALYZE --> YAML
    ANALYZE --> AI

    CLASS_ATTACH --> YAML
    CLASS_ATTACH --> AI

    VALIDATE --> YAML
    VALIDATE --> AI
    VALIDATE --> PY
    
    ORCH -. runtime state .-> ST